Alien-Tar-Size

tar LD_PRELOAD hack to compute size of tar file without reading and writing, provided as an Alien package

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Alien::Tar::Size

Additional documentation, support, and bug reports can be found at the MHFS
repository https://github.com/G4Vi/MHFS

